commit.message: Updated str.xml.in for Emoji and Japanese Acronym
Imported code.google.com/p/input-pad

Updated translations.

Updated ja.po

Fixed to use deprecated APIs in GTK 3.12

Changed xalign to halign.
Changed GtkAlignment to gtk_widget_set_margin_start().
Changed gtk_widget_override_background_color() to GtkCssProvider.
Fixed a build error of I_ since eek-types.h has the duplicated one.
Removed duplicated entry in str.xml
Fixed typo.
Updated uk.po
Updated ja.po
Updated str.xml.in for Emoji.
Added InputPadGtkViewport for many unicode tables.
Added some currencies.

Fixed a deprecated message of gtk_window_get_transient_for().

Fixed "GtkDialog mapped without a transient parent. ..."
Fixed the size of ContentsDialog.
https://git.gnome.org/browse/gtk+/commit/?id=c4ec89cf9d
Removed deprecated GtkTreeView::rules-hint property since GTK 3.14.

Fixed deprecated gtk-timeout-initial since GTK+ 3.10.

https://git.gnome.org/browse/gtk+/commit/?id=57fc8763e9

Fixed some memory leaks.

Called XFree() after XGetWindowProperty().
Called g_list_free() after gtk_container_get_children().
Do not call strdup for gtk_tree_store_set().

Used embedded GtkViewport in GtkScrolledWindow.

Used gtk_container_add() instead of calling gtk_viewport_new().
Used gtk_container_foreach() instead of foreach of GList.
Unref GdkPixbuf for a bug fix.
Added input_pad_gtk_button_get_label() since "label" property is not used.
Fixed icon sizes in the chartable.
Fixed deprecated GtkWidget.window
Do not call exit(3) in libinput-pad.so
Updated translations.
Changed deprecated GtkVBox to GtkBox in builder files.
